                </div>
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p>We offer a wide range of shipping services including same-day delivery, next-day delivery, standard shipping, international shipping, specialized shipping for fragile or temperature-sensitive items, and e-commerce fulfillment solutions.</p>
