              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                  <h3>How can I track my package?</h3>
                  <span class="accordion-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p>You can track your package by clicking on the "Track Package" button in the navigation and entering your tracking number. You'll see real-time updates on your package's location and estimated delivery time. You can also track packages through our mobile app or by signing into your account dashboard.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                  <h3>What should I do if my package is lost or damaged?</h3>
                  <span class="accordion-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p>If your package is lost or damaged, please contact our customer support team immediately at support@nowshipping.com or call 1-800-NOW-SHIP. We'll investigate the issue and process a claim if necessary. For packages with insurance, we'll process reimbursement according to our claims policy.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-panel" id="shipping-panel">
            <div class="accordion">
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                  <h3>How do I schedule a pickup?</h3>
                  <span class="accordion-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p>You can schedule a pickup through your account dashboard, our mobile app, or by calling our customer service. Select your preferred date and time window, and our courier will arrive to collect your package. For regular pickups, you can set up a recurring schedule.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                  <h3>What are the size and weight limits for packages?</h3>
                  <span class="accordion-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p>Our standard service accepts packages up to 70 lbs (32 kg) and with combined dimensions (length + width + height) not exceeding 130 inches (330 cm). For larger or heavier items, please contact our customer service for our freight shipping options.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                  <h3>How should I package my items for shipping?</h3>
                  <span class="accordion-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p>Use a sturdy box that's slightly larger than your item, with room for cushioning material. Wrap items individually and use packing materials like bubble wrap or packing peanuts to fill empty spaces. Seal the box securely with packing tape and apply shipping labels clearly. For fragile items, mark the package accordingly.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                  <h3>Can I change the delivery address after shipping?</h3>
                  <span class="accordion-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p>Yes, you can request an address change for packages that haven't been delivered yet. Log into your account, find the shipment, and select "Change Delivery Address." Additional fees may apply, and changes are subject to verification for security purposes.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-panel" id="international-panel">
